<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <style>
    body{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      padding-top: 20vh;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Nanum Gothic', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(#eee9f2, #f1edf4);
    }

    .box-container {
      background: white;
      padding: 5vh;
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .btn {
      display: block;
      padding: 11px;
      border-radius: 15rem;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #c43894;
    }
    .text-primary{
      color: #c43894;
    }

    .mt-5 {
      margin-top: 5vh;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="box-container">
      <h1>Activate your account!</h1>
      <div>Hey {{{ full_name }}},<br><br>
        Congrats once again, We invite you to officialy become an
        <strong class="text-primary">Awesomity Lab</strong> employee
        <br><br> You're one step closer to your career growth.
        Simply click the button below to verify your email address within one day.
        <br>
        Your password is : <strong>{{{ password }}}</strong>.
      </div>
      <a style="color: white" class="btn btn-primary mt-5" href={{{url}}} target="_blank">Activate my account now</a>
      <br>Can't see the button ? Use
      <a href={{{url}}} class="text-primary" target="_blank">this link</a>
      <br><br>
      Can't wait,<br><br>
      Your friends at <strong class="text-primary">Awesomity Lab!</strong>
      <br><br>
      Learn more about us <a href="https://awesomity.rw" class="text-primary" target="_blank">here</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>